#intro
  %h2.title Collaboratively create briefs and manage ideas with your team and your clients.
  .text
    %p ideapi allows you to create briefs, proposals and documents quickly, share them with your team and your clients, work together to create better content, share ideas and get things done.
    %p No more lost emails or to many versions of documents. Stay up to date and use ideapi as your place to simply create and share documents and ideas online.
    
    .signup
      = link_to "Sign Up Now", "/signup", :class => "try-button try-button-primary"          
      .meta
        for free!

  #promo-video
    :markdown
      <iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/11616621" width="500" height="300" frameborder="0"></iframe>
      

