      %li
        %h4 Work Together
        %p Invite who you need to work on a project and the system lets you create and collaborate together efficiently.
        
      %li
        %h4 Save Time
        %p Free creative minds to where when and where they want – and keep tabs on their input.

      %li
        %h4 Stay in Control
        %p Manage your team and your clients by dictating who can see what.

      %li
        %h4 Keep it Safe
        %p ideapi stores your information, ideas and attachments securely, so you do not have to worry about them. Never lose and idea again. You never know when it will be useful.

      %li
        %h4 Be clear
        %p Give clients as much or as little visibility of your process. Include them to collaborate, approve or just give them a topline on what you need them to see.

      %li
        %h4 Waste less
        %p Keep briefs and the ideas online, avoid reams of printer paper being sacrificed needlessly.

      %li.last-benefit
        %h4 Re-write less
        %p Create templates for documents that are created regularly – both section titles and section text can be added to templates so less needs to be re-written.
      
